main event: Two white males observed an unidentified flying object in California, Missouri on January 30, 1967.
interesting points: The object was seen moving horizontally and disappeared toward the north,The object's motion was evaluated as too slow for a plane and too fast for a helicopter,The estimated observation time was about 4-5 minutes,There was no record of any aircraft in the area at the time of the sighting,The witnesses described seeing bright lights cycling quickly with no sound involved.
sighted object: one unidentified flying object with bright lights
